---
---

<section id="hero" class="min-h-screen flex items-center section-padding pt-20 md:pt-0">
  <div class="section-container w-full">
    <!-- Status pill -->
    <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full text-xs font-medium mb-8 border"
      style="background-color: var(--bg-secondary); border-color: var(--border); color: var(--text-soft);">
      <span
        class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full flex-shrink-0"
        style="background-color: #22C55E; animation: pulseDot 2s ease-in-out infinite;"
      ></span>
      Available for mentorship &amp; speaking
    </div>

    <!-- Headline -->
    <h1
      class="font-semibold text-balance mb-6 animate-slide-up"
      style="font-size: clamp(2.25rem, 5vw, 3.5rem); line-height: 1.1; letter-spacing: -0.02em; color: var(--text); opacity: 0; animation-fill-mode: forwards;"
    >
      Designing with <span style="color: var(--accent);">purpose.</span><br />
      Leading with empathy.
    </h1>

    <!-- Bio -->
    <p
      class="body-text max-w-prose text-base mb-10 animate-slide-up"
      style="animation-delay: 0.1s; opacity: 0; animation-fill-mode: forwards;"
    >
      I'm Jonathan — Sr. Product Design Manager at Docusign, educator at BrainStation,
      and co-leader of Friends of Figma Miami. I help teams build thoughtful, accessible,
      and deeply human experiences.
    </p>

    <!-- CTAs -->
    <div
      class="flex flex-wrap gap-3 mb-12 animate-slide-up"
      style="animation-delay: 0.2s; opacity: 0; animation-fill-mode: forwards;"
    >
      <a href="#work" class="btn-primary">
        View my work
        <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
          <path d="M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7"/>
        </svg>
      </a>
      <a href="mailto:hello@jonathanruiz.dev" class="btn-ghost">Say hello</a>
    </div>

    <!-- Scripture card -->
    <div
      class="max-w-prose animate-slide-up"
      style="animation-delay: 0.3s; opacity: 0; animation-fill-mode: forwards;"
    >
      <div
        class="px-5 py-4 rounded-lg border-l-2"
        style="background-color: var(--bg-secondary); border-left-color: var(--accent); border-top: 1px solid var(--border); border-right: 1px solid var(--border); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);"
      >
        <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed italic mb-1.5" style="color: var(--text-soft);">
          "Whatever you do, work at it with all your heart, as working for the Lord."
        </p>
        <p class="text-xs font-medium" style="font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace; color: var(--accent);">
          — Colossians 3:23
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
